{"itemid":2049,"subject":"Wild Card Blogs and Samples","event":"A few odds and ends on the Wild Cards front...\r\n\r\nFor those curious about the history of Wild Cards development in Hollywood, Melinda Snodgrass has a new post up on the Wild Cards blog at http://www.wildcardsworld.com/its-a-long-and-winding-road/\r\n\r\nOver at Tor.com, the Wild Cards ReRead is well under way, presided over by Katy Rask.  They are discussing book one.  Join in at http://www.tor.com/2017/03/02/wild-cards-reveals-a-dark-reflection-of-our-post-war-reality/\r\n\r\nMeanwhile, on my own website, I've got a new sample up from the next Wild Cards original in the pipeline, MISSISSIPPI ROLL.  Get a taste of \"Wingless Angel\" by John Jos. Miller; Carnifex and the Midnight Angel in New Orleans.  You'll find it at http://www.georgerrmartin.com/wild-cards-excerpt/\r\n\r\nHappy reading, aces.","ditemid":524688,"eventtime":"2017-03-06 16:26:00","props":{"current_mood":"satisfied","current_location":"Santa Fe","taglist":"wild cards","crosspost_tw_log":"[Mon Mar  6 23:26:35 2017]R [Mon Mar  6 23:26:36 2017]https://twitter.com/GRRMspeaking/status/838893606077366274 ","current_moodid":26,"homepage_reposted":63986505,"commentalter":1492274349,"opt_lockcomments":1,"crosspost_tw":"https://twitter.com/GRRMspeaking/status/838893606077366274","picture_keyword":"lohengrin","opt_screening":"F","likes_first_notify":1,"revnum":1,"personifi_tags":"nterms:yes","interface":"web","langs":"{\"languages\":[[\"eng\",0.657811865476196]],\"detector\":\"Lingua-YALI:0.015\",\"updated\":1488842825}","og_image":"http://l-files.livejournal.net/og_image/7059164/2049?v=1489177739","revtime":1489177739},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2017-03-06 23:26:34","anum":144,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/524688.html","event_timestamp":1488817560,"reply_count":5,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/126028487/77709202","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/524688.html?threa